<div class="com-share" data-id="12521" data-title="《郑钧想要靠一款 App 重新激活音乐行业，听上去有点理想主义》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/12521/medium/12521.jpg?1437626470" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/12521.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
